Package: catSurv
Title: Computerized Adaptive Testing
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person(given = "Jacob M.", family = "Montgomery", email = "jacob.montgomery@wustl.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides methods of computerized adaptive testing for survey researchers. Includes functionality for data fit with the latent trait, Birnbaum`s three parameter, the graded response, or the generalized partial credit model.  Additionally, includes several ability parameter estimation and item selection routines.  During item selection, all calculations are done in compiled C++ code.
Depends:
	R(>= 3.3.2)
